      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in great shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-loved. If you're looking for a reliable car that still looks sharp and handles beautifully, this is the one for you! I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road whenever you are. Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
