    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been properly sorted with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded polyurethane bushings to ensure structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and precise valve clearance adjustments. This is a driver-spec example that maintains excellent turn-in response and the communicative steering feedback synonymous with the E46 platform.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
