    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a beautifully maintained example of a modern classic that balances performance with everyday utility. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, and it shows in the details. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, having been regularly waxed and garaged; while you might find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving, there are no major dings or scratches to speak of. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with supple leather seating that shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. We recently performed a full fluid flush and fitted a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires. It shifts smoothly, brakes confidently, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a turnkey vehicle ready for its next chapter, perfect for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect.",
